description:
The cast of Yellowjackets watch back iconic moments from the series and drop some real tea on what actually happened on set. ☕ Catch up on seasons 1 and 2 of Yellowjackets now! Featuring Courtney Eaton, Simone Kessell, Samantha Hanratty, Christina Ricci, Jasmin Savoy Brown, Tawny Cypress, Liv Hewson, Lauren Ambrose, Sophie Nélisse and Melanie Lynskey.

Yellowjackets Season 3 is streaming February 14 with the Paramount+ with SHOWTIME plan.

About Yellowjackets: Part survival epic, part psychological horror and part coming-of-age drama, this is the story of a team of wildly talented high school girls' soccer players who survive a plane crash deep in the remote northern wilderness. The series chronicles their descent from a complicated but thriving team to savage clans, while also tracking the lives they’ve attempted to piece back together 25 years later. What began in the wilderness is far from over. Starring Melanie Lynskey, Tawny Cypress, with Christina Ricci and Juliette Lewis.
